milestones.description: Kallis has broken the record for most sixes (95) in ODIs for SA, going past Hansie Cronje's 94

stories.title: Prince trumps Pietersen to secure SA victory
stories.subTitle: South Africa v England, 7th ODI, Centurion
stories.summary: Ashwell Prince overcame a testing spell from Steve Harmison, and Jacques Kallis continued to tick off the runs in his own unhurried manner, as South Africa survived a mid-innings blip to secure a comfortable three-wicket victory
